Class CoordFunction2D

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.caom2.caom2.wcs.CoordFunction2D
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
@Embeddable @VoDml(id="caom2:caom2.wcs.CoordFunction2D", role=dataType) public class CoordFunction2D extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
a two-dimensional (linear) WCS coordinate transformation function; this can be used to compute the world coordinates of every pixel. dataType: CoordFunction2D
